</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The white space between images is not equal 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Functional logging (if available)</b>
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No logging available which can pinpoint to this case.
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">ADAM-triggers</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No available ADAM-triggers 
</p></section><section id="GUID-DDCC1BB0-B402-4010-9156-67DB737F3DE5" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Analyze/Repair</title><fig id="GUID-15CB5C79-9E9D-4DBE-8F24-33A1E3A75CC2" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-58DE4B06-C208-49C9-876C-12C4F1ACB05A-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-58DE4B06-C208-49C9-876C-12C4F1ACB05A-svg.svg"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-BB9BDDD1-E29C-42C5-BF10-2854E3AE4223" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Steps explanation</title><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-D963269B-E108-446A-A212-4581FEAA8740" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="20*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col4" colnum="4" colwidth="30*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Type 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">To do 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check whether the media is calibrated 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">In case the media isn’t calibrated an exclamation sign is visible in the UI. 
</p><fig id="GUID-CBA39104-2BE0-4030-B562-51916E04A137" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-51A04FF7-0AFC-4927-984F-8E1D3D278823-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-51A04FF7-0AFC-4927-984F-8E1D3D278823-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Perform media calibration including the leading edge 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Cut media before calibration 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check whether the images are stacked via the controller 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Stack images via the controller 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-2513E5DF-C282-453D-9841-6E539DB0EB51" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Evaluate/Prevention</title><p class="- topic/p ">Stack images in the same job to guarantee a uniform distance between the images. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-987F83F9-80F0-41BC-B82B-BB16DA268203" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Background info</title><p class="- topic/p ">The white space between images (distance) is determined by the customer via the controller (eg : ONYX). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The white space between images of the same job are managed by the controller and therefor yellow or black markers are used during media movement between images. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In case images are send via different jobs the distance between the jobs is only managed by moving the media. This movement is less accurate compared to using the markers.
</p></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-00803BE3-C849-4315-B1B2-2BBE04B8DBA4.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Solutions</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
